(309, 0, '', 0, '<p>js执行原理：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="https://heyingye.github.io/" target="_blank">https://heyingye.github.io/</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>苍青浪：<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/cangqinglang/" target="_blank">https://www.cnblogs.com/cangqinglang/</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>NodeJS 充分利用多核CPU服务器处理高并发请求：<a href="http://zuoming.iteye.com/blog/1457955" target="_blank">http://zuoming.iteye.com/blog/1457955</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>NodeJS的代码调试和性能调优：<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/hustskyking/p/how-to-build-a-https-server.html" target="_blank">https://www.cnblogs.com/hustskyking/p/how-to-build-a-https-server.html</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>异步I/O的理解：<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/jacie_chaochao/article/details/50119363" target="_blank">https://blog.csdn.net/jacie_chaochao/article/details/50119363</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I/O基本概念：<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/java_pengjin/article/details/79771292" target="_blank">https://blog.csdn.net/java_pengjin/article/details/79771292</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>图解I/O的五种模型：<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/budongshu/p/5117584.html" target="_blank">https://www.cnblogs.com/budongshu/p/5117584.html</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>进程、线程、多线程相关总结：<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/fuchongjundream/p/3829508.html" target="_blank">https://www.cnblogs.com/fuchongjundream/p/3829508.html</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n深入理解进程和线程：<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/tiankong101/p/4229584.html" target="_blank">https://www.cnblogs.com/tiankong101/p/4229584.html</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>JavaScript 运行机制详解：再谈Event Loop:<br />\r\n<a href="http://www.ruanyifeng.com/blog/2014/10/event-loop.html" target="_blank">http://www.ruanyifeng.com/blog/2014/10/event-loop.html</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>js与Nodejs的单线程和异步--初探:<br />\r\n<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/wanghuohuo/p/7156323.html" target="_blank">https://www.cnblogs.com/wanghuohuo/p/7156323.html</a></p>\r\n', '2018-12-05 08:09:11', '2018-12-07 17:42:02', 4, 0),
